data.description: Wow!  What a find!  This cute home has options - use the whole house for yourself or use the basement for a 1 bed/1 bath rental w/it's own entrance - just have to put a door back in place and it's ready to go!  Oversized garage with lots of space.  New water heater, patio has been enlarged and sewer line has been cleaned and replaced, electric panel/box has been moved and updated and 2 bathrooms have been updated in the last year.
